Date: Mon, 16 Aug 1999 13:32:01 -0400 (EDT)
From: Helmut Albrecht <halbrec@emory.edu>

Regarding the blinding disease in elephants. Did you ever obtain a biopsy
for microscopy? Electron microscopy might be helpful if LM (Light
Microscopy) does not give diagnostic clues. How about microsporidia?
---
Helmut Albrecht, M.D.
